- chance to show the impact of being afflicted
- they hve to be interesting, and not the same

- effect of each

  - hallucinations

    - intelligence -= 50%
    - 10% chance to stop to punch at anything
    - damage += 10%
    - energy recovery += 50%
    - chance to desperate retreat += 50%
    - chance to rampage += 50%

  - injured
    - start and max stamina reduced by 2
    - damage taken += 50%
    - have to do nothing from wincing in pain
    - +50% chance to rampage
  - sick
    - agression to 1 -= 50%
    - start and max stamina reduced by 2
    - damage dealt -50%
    - have to stop to sick
    - energy regen rate - 50%
